function Start()

-- Disabling the chest so it can't be opened yet.
	if Hydra.ActorIsValid(ID_CHEST) then
		Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(ID_CHEST, true)
	end

-- Enabling spawners.
	for i, idAllSpawner in ipairs(T_ALL_SPAWNERS) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAllSpawner) then
			Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(idAllSpawner, false)
		end
	end

-- Proxy monster to hold affixs for the chest.	
	idAffixMonster = Hydra.ActorSpawnActor(S_AFFIX_SURROGATE, idSelf, false, 0,0, Hydra.MR_ELITE)

-- Chest knockback and vfx.	
	Hydra.ActorTriggerPowerAtFeet(idChest, S_KNOCKBACK_POWER)
	Hydra.BuffApplyToTarget(S_KNOCKBACK_POWER, "CHEST_VFX", idChest)

end

function Start()

-- ActorKill all remaining Spawners
	for i, idAllSpawner in ipairs(T_ALL_SPAWNERS) do
		if Hydra.ActorIsValid(idAllSpawner) then 
			Hydra.ActorDelete(idAllSpawner)
		end
	end

-- Remove the affix monster.	
	Hydra.ActorDelete(idAffixMonster)
	
end

-- Enabling the chest and removing the vfx.
Hydra.ActorGizmoSetDisabled(ID_CHEST, false)
Hydra.BuffRemove(S_KNOCKBACK_POWER, "CHEST_VFX", idChest)

function Start(idActorPlayer, idActorGizmo)

-- Reward event loot
	if bChestReward == 1 then
		Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActor(idActorGizmo, S_TREASURE_HEROIC)
	else
		Hydra.TreasureClassDropAtActor(idActorGizmo, S_TREASURE_NORMAL)
	end
	
end
